Sentencas: An interlayer of samaria doped ceria(SDC)
Titulo: Improvement of the performance of fuel cells anodes with Sm3+ Ddoped CeO2 interlayer

Sentencas: was prepared between Ni-SDC composite electrode and LSGM(La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O3) electrolyte using screen-printing method to improve the performance of Ni anodes.
Titulo: Improvement of the performance of fuel cells anodes with Sm3+ Ddoped CeO2 interlayer

Sentencas: The effect of this interlayer on the performance of anode as well as the cell was studied using various electrochemical techniques.
Titulo: Improvement of the performance of fuel cells anodes with Sm3+ Ddoped CeO2 interlayer

Sentencas: The results show that addition of the SDC interlayer reduced the anodic over-potential significantly, however, the ohmic resistance of the cell with an SDC interlayer increased, which leaded to a decrease of the power output.
Titulo: Improvement of the performance of fuel cells anodes with Sm3+ Ddoped CeO2 interlayer

Sentencas: The electrochemical oxidation of H-2 on Ni-SDC anodes was controlled by two processes, which corresponded to two arcs in the impedance spectra.
Titulo: Improvement of the performance of fuel cells anodes with Sm3+ Ddoped CeO2 interlayer

Sentencas: The high frequency arc decreased with the addition of SDC interlayer, and could correspond to the electrochemical reaction at three-phase-boundary(TPB) or the transfer of oxygen ions from LSGM to SDC.
Titulo: Improvement of the performance of fuel cells anodes with Sm3+ Ddoped CeO2 interlayer

Sentencas: The low frequency arc showed no dependency on the addition of SDC, and could be related to the adsorption and diffusion of H-2 at the surface of electrode.
Titulo: Improvement of the performance of fuel cells anodes with Sm3+ Ddoped CeO2 interlayer

Sentencas: The cells with an SDC interlayer showed much better stability compared with the cell using single layer anode, and the performance of the cell with Ni-SDC/SDC(1573 K) anode was higher than the cell with a single layer Ni-SDC anode after long time running.
Titulo: Improvement of the performance of fuel cells anodes with Sm3+ Ddoped CeO2 interlayer
